+## Scenario — demo runtime state and local traces
+
+```
+Given I want deterministic demo files and local debug traces
+ When I set AUGCHATD_DATA_DIR=/tmp/augchatd-data
+  And I set AUGCHATD_TRACE_DIR=/tmp/augchatd-traces
+ Then demo runtime state is written under /tmp/augchatd-data
+  And local JSONL debug traces are written under /tmp/augchatd-traces
+  And no metrics endpoint, distributed tracing backend, or audit-log surface is enabled
+```
+
 ## Why this matters
 
 The two-mode design lets evaluation cost stay low without splitting the chat code path or shipping a separate artifact.
